Here’s a warm and concise announcement you can send to your team:


---

Subject: Great News – [Name] Welcomes a Baby Girl!

Hi everyone,

I’m delighted to share some wonderful news — [Name] and their family have welcomed a baby girl! Both mother and baby are doing well.

Please join me in congratulating [Name] on this exciting new chapter!

Best,
[Your Name]


---

Would you like it to sound a bit more personal or keep it short and professional like this?

